{"type":"text","timestamp":1777038255980,"sessionID":"ses_24044e3ebffeI2SkdKQLUEjELW","part":{"id":"prt_dbfbbd47f001urYRzsB0M3DGJT","messageID":"msg_dbfbbcc590010jmQ5UUipY8d2K","sessionID":"ses_24044e3ebffeI2SkdKQLUEjELW","type":"text","text":"`index.html` is ready. Here's what's included:\n\n**Controls**\n- Arrow keys or WASD to steer\n- `R` to restart at any time\n- Click the button on the overlay to start/restart\n\n**Features**\n- 24×24 grid canvas, all inline HTML/CSS/JS\n- Score + personal best tracking (persists across restarts in the session)\n- Game over detection: wall and self-collision\n- Start screen and game-over overlay with final score\n- 180° reversal prevention (can't go directly backwards)\n\n**Visual polish**\n- Dark theme with subtle grid lines\n- Snake uses a green→cyan gradient from head to tail\n- Head has a soft inner highlight\n- Food has a radial glow and gradient fill\n- Rounded segment corners\n- Overlay uses backdrop blur\n- Button has a hover lift effect","time":{"start":1777038251135,"end":1777038255979}}}
